','','','2011-04-18 16:29:13','2011-04-18 16:29:13','',1610,'http://broadstreetdata.com/index.php/1610-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1522,4,'2011-03-01 20:22:01','2011-03-01 20:22:01','\r\n<!-- .question { display: block; float: left; padding: 10px 0; width: 100%} .yes, .no { float: left; width: 15%; } -->\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Geneva, Arial, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"color: #cc3333;\">The Instant Data Maturity Benchmark </span></span></span></h2>\r\n<h3><span class=\"parHeading3DarkGrey\"><span class=\"darkgrey3\">This simple review will help identify where you are on the arc of data management ... and where you are going to go. </span></span></h3>\r\n<span class=\"parHeading3DarkGrey\"><span class=\"darkgrey3\">Hundreds of companies have benefited - it\'s quick, confidential and reliable.\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;\">If you\'re not sure about an answer leave it blank.</span>\r\n\r\n<form id=\"survey_form\" style=\"text-align: left;\" action=\".\" enctype=\"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\" method=\"post\">\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre simple tools like spread sheets the primary way data is being used on the desktop?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwC0\" title=\"Simple Desktop Tools\" name=\"Are simple tools like spread sheets the primary way data is being used on the desktop?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwC0\" title=\"Simple Desktop Tools\" name=\"Are simple tools like spread sheets the primary way data is being used on the desktop?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nIs data proliferating through your company without control?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Is data proliferating through your company without control?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Is data proliferating through your company without control?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre there quality inconsistencies in the data you work with?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Are there quality inconsistencies in the data you work with?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Are there quality inconsistencies in the data you work with?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nDo you have defined and usable reference or master data such as client, address, counter party, item?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Do you have defined and usable reference or master data such as client, address, counter party, item?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Do you have defined and usable reference or master data such as client, address, counter party, item?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre you working with third party data?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRJ\" title=\"Third Party Data\" name=\"Are you working with third party data?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRJ\" title=\"Third Party Data\" name=\"Are you working with third party data?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nIs there an enterprise data model available (something that shows the relationships between data but across systems)?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRO\" title=\"Enterprise Data Model\" name=\"Is there an enterprise data model available (something that shows the relationships between data but across systems)?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRO\" title=\"Enterprise Data Model\" name=\"Is there an enterprise data model available (something that shows the relationships between data but across systems)?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre there standard business terms definitions used across the business?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" title=\"Standard Business Terms\" name=\"Are there standard business terms definitions used across the business?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" title=\"Standard Business Terms\" name=\"Are there standard business terms definitions used across the business?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre there standards for data quality?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRY\" title=\"Data Quality Standards\" name=\"Are there standards for data quality?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRY\" title=\"Data Quality Standards\" name=\"Are there standards for data quality?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nAre there standards for data security, access rights, audit and use?\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRi\" title=\"Standards for data security\" name=\"Are there standards for data security, access rights, audit and use?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRi\" title=\"Standards for data security\" name=\"Are there standards for data security, access rights, audit and use?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nDo you have standa