Standard Business Terms\" name=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" title=\"Standard Business Terms\" name=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<div class=\"question\">Are there standards for data quality?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRY\" title=\"Data Quality Standards\" name=\"00N80000003mwRY\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRY\" title=\"Data Quality Standards\" name=\"00N80000003mwRY\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<div class=\"question\">Are there standards for data security, access rights, audit and use?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRi\" title=\"Standards for data security\" name=\"00N80000003mwRi\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRi\" title=\"Standards for data security\" name=\"00N80000003mwRi\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<div class=\"question\">Do you have standard tools for integration such as middleware?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLW\" title=\"Middleware\" name=\"00N80000003mwLW\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLW\" title=\"Middleware\" name=\"00N80000003mwLW\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<div class=\"question\">Is it time consuming and expensive to integrate systems?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwSC\" title=\"Time Consuming Integration\" name=\"00N80000003mwSC\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwSC\" title=\"Time Consuming Integration\" name=\"00N80000003mwSC\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<div class=\"question\">Do you have defined roles and responsibilities for the management of data?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\">