le, consolidated master repository (for the most important reference data like Customers, Securities, etc) at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nDo you have a Data Steward at your firm?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Do you have a Data Steward at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Do you have a Data Steward at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nDo you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Do you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Do you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nCan your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Can your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Can your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nCan you confidently state the data quality level of the data provided by your data suppliers/vendors?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRJ\" title=\"Third Party Data\" name=\"Can you confidently state the data quality level of the data provided by your data suppliers/vendors?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRJ\" title=\"Third Party Data\" name=\"Can you confidently state the data quality level of the data provided by your data suppliers/vendors?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nDo your main business users understand all the data you have, and can easily access it (via application or reporting tool)?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRO\" title=\"Enterprise Data Model\" name=\"Do your main business users understand all the data you have, and can easily access it (via application or reporting tool)?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRO\" title=\"Enterprise Data Model\" name=\"Do your main business users understand all the data you have, and can easily access it (via application or reporting tool)?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nDo you have your business logic to process and load all vendor’s data files, located in one place, and documented?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" title=\"Standard Business Terms\" name=\"Do you have your business logic to process and load all vendor’s data files, located in one place, and documented?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPJ\" title=\"Standard Business Terms\" name=\"Do you have your business logic to process and load all vendor’s data files, located in one place, and documented?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question\">\n\nRight now, in all your systems, are you able to identify suspect or bad data, when it was loaded and where it came from?\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRY\" title=\"Data Quality Standards\" name=\"Right now, in all your systems, are you able to identify suspect or bad data, when it was loaded and where it came from?\" type