ngle, consolidated master repository (for the most important reference data like Customers, Securities, etc) at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nDo you have a Data Steward at your firm?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Do you have a Data Steward at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLQ\" title=\"Data Proliferation\" name=\"Do you have a Data Steward at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nDo you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Do you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwLV\" title=\"Data Quality Inconsistencies\" name=\"Do you have a Data Governance Council or team at your firm?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nCan your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Can your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"Yes\" /> Yes</div>\r\n<div class=\"no\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwPI\" title=\"Master Data\" name=\"Can your firm deploy an updated ETL process to accommodate a significant change in a vendor’s feed in 1 week or less?\" type=\"radio\" value=\"No\" /> No</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question\">\r\n\r\nCan you confidently state the data quality level of the data provided by your data suppliers/vendors?<br/>\r\n<div class=\"yes\"><input id=\"00N80000003mwRJ\" title=\"Third Party Data\" name=\"C